		(object Operation "TEST_WCGetActValue"
		    quid       	"3F9672BD034B"
		    documentation 	
|DESCRIPTION:
|TEST_WCGetActValue calculates the state of a voice coil drive in the next time interval if an electrical current Ia is applied to the coil and the direction of movement is dfa (1=fw, -1=rv). The state of the vc in the last time interval is passed as a paramter.
|
|INPUT:
|p_Wdg_Volt: DAC Value [Digit]
|p_dfa: direction of movement (1=fw, -1=rv)
		    
		    stereotype 	"void"
		    parameters 	(list Parameters
			(object Parameter "p_Wdg_Volt"
			    type       	"int")
			(object Parameter "p_dfa"
			    type       	"int")
			(object Parameter "p_clast"
			    type       	"DWORD&")
			(object Parameter "p_cdiff"
			    type       	"DWORD&")
			(object Parameter "p_cp"
			    type       	"int&"))
		    result     	"int"
		    concurrency 	"Sequential"
		    opExportControl 	"Public"
		    uid        	1066825080)
